{"tid":443604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又有！燒焊工房署地盤工字鐵砸頭亡","createTime":"2017-10-21T16:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T12:16:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1c31c96e63a4f10aee69e0c60ffbca98d70a1aa2","tid":443604,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"東涌昨日發生奪命工傷，36歲姓黃燒焊工人，昨午3時許在裕東路房署地盤工作時，被一支吊起的工字鐵擊中頭部昏迷，由救護車送北大嶼山醫院急救後，再轉送瑪嘉烈醫院留醫。黃父得知地盤無報警，晚上10時許在醫院報案。黃延至今凌晨不治，警方接報後到有關地盤調查，案件列作工業意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171021/bkn-20171021231042067-1021_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171021%2Fbkn-20171021231042067-1021_00822_001.html&d=LuN311ryFqadCm5aAoakJ10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4500c7d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171021/bkn-20171021231042067-1021_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b05b06b3ec4cafeaa19e69176f0d58ab64191cb2","tid":443604,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"地盤=?"},{"pid":"80ef2569e36c9675a8eeef243da170f1f8605b32","tid":443604,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T21:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地盤=?</blockquote><br />\nDeath<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da358d3a2157a93b441a365741776fe5ef3e22da","tid":443604,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T21:44:20.000Z","msg":"邊間main con? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d35f4929f68c02b002b972947e94700099ab70e","tid":443604,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T22:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間main con? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係保安調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd092afbd914dd4d2821ae5